00:42:09,028 --> 00:42:10,389
You look then at the project scope.

887
00:42:10,389 --> 00:42:12,650
Can we actually pull off the value proposition

888
00:42:12,650 --> 00:42:13,410
with this vision?

889
00:42:15,166 --> 00:42:16,407
up to the prototype phase.

