975
00:46:50,929 --> 00:46:52,491
people are actually watching on YouTube.

976
00:46:54,438 --> 00:46:56,539
Also, a game that creates stories,

977
00:46:56,539 --> 00:46:59,260
so you will tell your friends what happened in the game,

978
00:46:59,260 --> 00:47:02,642
and you will be intrigued to create more things that

979
00:47:02,642 --> 00:47:04,262
are happening and engaging in the game.

980
00:47:04,262 --> 00:47:08,444
And the most important factor of all,

981
00:47:08,444 --> 00:47:11,185
let the people who create value in your game

982
00:47:11,185 --> 00:47:13,046
also make money from it.

983
00:47:13,046 --> 00:47:14,367
You can split it up in between you,

984
00:47:14,367 --> 00:47:16,048
because after all, it's your game,

985
00:47:16,048 --> 00:47:18,229
so you should have some of the money.

986
00:47:18,229 --> 00:47:20,890
But there are companies who are blocking people

987
00:47:20,890 --> 00:47:22,751
from putting up YouTube videos as well.

988
00:47:22,751 --> 00:47:23,231
Don't do that.

989
00:47:24,657 --> 00:47:25,137
suicide.

